snippet.title: Armored Core 6: Fires of Rubicon - Launch Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description: Check out the launch trailer for Armored Core 6: Fires of Rubicon, the long awaited sixth entry in the epic mech series by From Software. You can jump into this likely brutal game on August 26, 2023 on PS5, PS4, Xbox One, Xbox Series X and PC.
